  "title": "✈️🌍 Sales & Marketing (Travel Opportunities)",
  "description": "<p>📍 Singapore | Full-Time | Entry-Level</p><p>Royal Organisation is looking for driven individuals who enjoy working with people and are excited by opportunities to travel while building a career in sales and marketing.</p><p>You’ll represent clients at event sites, engage customers face-to-face, and learn how successful campaigns are executed — with <strong>regional and international travel opportunities</strong> for performers.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Individuals who want growth, exposure, and an energetic lifestyle alongside their career.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements / What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p><ul><li>🌱 Open-minded, adaptable, and eager to learn</li><li>🗣 Comfortable interacting with people face-to-face</li><li>🔥 Energetic, driven, and open to new experiences</li></ul></p><p><strong>Responsibilities / What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>🎪 Execute event-based marketing campaigns</li><li>🤝 Engage customers and represent client brands</li><li>👥 Work with a team to achieve campaign goals</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits / What You’ll Gain</strong></p><p><ul><li>✈️ Regional & international travel opportunities</li><li>🎯 1-on-1 mentorship and continuous coaching</li><li>💰 Performance-based rewards and growth</li></ul></p>",
